title: Navigate forwards to a collapsed select-only combobox in reading mode
instructions: With the reading cursor on the 'Navigate forwards from here' link, navigate to the 'Favorite Fruit' Combobox.

title: Navigate backwards to a collapsed select-only combobox in reading mode
instructions: With the reading cursor on the 'Navigate backwards from here' link, navigate to the 'Favorite Fruit' Combobox.

title: Request information about a collapsed select-only combobox in reading mode
instructions: With the reading cursor on the 'Favorite Fruit' combobox, read information about the combobox.

title: Open a collapsed select-only combobox in reading mode
instructions: With the reading cursor on the combobox, open the combobox.
assertions: stateComboboxExpanded rolePopupListbox namePopupFavoriteFruit textFocusedOptionPopupChooseFruitIsNotConveyed stateFocusedOptionPopupSelected positionFocusedOptionPopup1 numberOptionsPopup13

title: Open a collapsed select-only combobox to the first option in interaction mode
instructions: With focus on the combobox, open the combobox and set focus to the first option.
assertions: stateComboboxExpanded rolePopupListbox namePopupFavoriteFruit textFocusedOptionPopupChooseFruit stateFocusedOptionPopupSelectedIsNotConveyed positionFocusedOptionPopup1 numberOptionsPopup13

title: Open a collapsed select-only combobox to a specific option in interaction mode
instructions: With focus on the combobox, open the combobox and set focus on a specific option by typing a printable character.
assertions: stateComboboxExpanded rolePopupListbox namePopupFavoriteFruit textFocusedOptionPopupApple stateFocusedOptionPopupNotSelected positionFocusedOptionPopup2 numberOptionsPopup13

title: Open a collapsed select-only combobox to the last option in interaction mode
instructions: With focus on the combobox, open the combobox and set focus on the last option.
assertions: stateComboboxExpanded rolePopupListbox namePopupFavoriteFruit textFocusedOptionPopupHuckleberry stateFocusedOptionPopupNotSelected positionFocusedOptionPopup13 numberOptionsPopup13
